.TH DCR-RUN 1 "2026-06-02" "dcr 0.7.0" "DCR Manual"
.SH NAME
dcr-run \- Build and run a DCR project
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B dcr run
[\fB\-\-debug\fR | \fB\-\-release\fR]
[\fB\-\-target\fR \fI<triple>\fR]
[\fB\-\-force\fR]
[\fB\-\-clean\fR]
[\fB\-\-verbose\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Builds and runs the project. Only available for projects with
\fBkind = "bin"\fR.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B \-\-debug
Run with debug profile (default).
.TP
.B \-\-release
Run with release profile.
.TP
.B \-\-target \fI<triple>\fR
Cross-compile for the given target.
.TP
.B \-\-force
Force a full rebuild.
.TP
.B \-\-clean
Clean before building.
.TP
.B \-\-verbose
Print detailed build output.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR dcr (1),
.BR dcr-build (1)
